The coupon on the 80 mln ECU, five yearequity warrant eurobond for Japan's Wacoal Corp has been fixedat the indicated 1-1/2 pct, bookrunner Banque Paribas CapitalMarkets said.    The exercise price was set at 1,323 yen per share,representing a premium of 2.56 pct over today's closing priceof 1,290 yen. The foreign exchange rate was set at 167.11 yento the ECU. REUTER&#3;